data.description: 300 CILE CHURCH ROAD .... this picturesque, wonderfully spacious, 4 BEDROOM, 2.5 BATHHOME offers to you MORE than peace   tranquility. Tucked away on 7.45 ACRES, with a 3400+ sq. foot SHOP, custom cabinets, granite countertops, gas cooktop, rustic ''lodge'' feel, THIS ONE is HOME!  Add to that a 72 x 8 COVERED FRONT PORCH, livestock fencing, 2 HVAC units and a METAL ROOF and this one is a MUST TOUR!
